         I think the hp versus int argument really only gets into it's own for the level 55 + necro but IMHO you could do with a couple of changes.</P><P>At level 40 I think the extra 6 int you have over 200 makes a very very small difference to your mana pool. I would dump the +5 int rings and load up with 2 crafted 6ac / 65hp rings. The extra 130HP will make a significant difference to your life expectancy both during fights and during medding.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
