        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         people NEED to stop comparing yourself to everyone else....and instead compare yourself to others whos playstyle/guild/EQ alotted time are similar.  It s ridiculous for a lvl 60 in a small guild who plays here and there to compare his/her  gear/hp/manapool  to an "uberguilds" or "powergamers" such as Zaar or Savan...instead look more specificly at others with simialar habits and ask.....Do i run out of mana or Hps more often.......now adjust your gear accordlying to that....a lvl 30 necro with 2khp may want to get more mana and drop a few hps......and vise versa a lvl X with 255 int and all +mana gear who can cast for ever may want to get rid of some int and add hps.......what works for a lvl 60 necro doesnt mean it work for a 50 40 30 20 10 and what works for a 10 20 30 may not work for for a 40 50 60....i guess to sum it up....adjust YOUR gear in a way that meet YOUR playstyle and keeps you alive and with mana AND NOT always try to do match what UBER NECRO X is doing,,chances are you dont play the same way and therefore have differnt needs.</P><P>Sallymanders<BR>Warlock of Povar<BR>Triton<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=161288" target="_blank">MY GEAR</a></P><P>My dirty twink- <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=265598" target="_blank">Idovudu</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
